            <ul>
              <li><strong>NaProTECHNOLOGY (Natural Procreative Technology) diagnoses and treats the underlying conditions</strong> behind reproductive health problems using the Creighton Model FertilityCare System as a real-time diagnostic tool.<sup><a href="#ref-5">5</a></sup></li>
